OL,6,FWatch the police dashcam footage of
OL,7,Fofficers in pursuit of Jack Lowrey.
OL,9,FA driver who dropped his speed to only
OL,10,F10mph as he sought to flee police
OL,11,Fduring a night-time west Cumbria chase
OL,12,Fhas been handed an immediate prison
OL,13,Fsentence.
OL,15,FJack Lowrey, 21, came to the attention
OL,16,Fof officers on 11 January, 2025 after
OL,17,Fhe was seen driving erratically as if
OL,18,F"under the influence of something",
OL,19,FCarlisle Crown Court heard.
