OL,3,CWATCH: 10mph danger driver handed
OL,4,Cprison sentence
OL,6,FLowrey was behind the wheel of a red
OL,7,FFord Focus courtesy vehicle ` provided
OL,8,Fby garage staff to his father ` which
OL,9,Fhe took without permission.
OL,11,FLowrey drove away from one police
OL,12,Fconstable who initially saw him
OL,13,Fstationary on Moorclose Road in
OL,14,FWorkington. Lowrey then headed south
OL,15,Ftowards Whitehaven, where a second
OL,16,Fofficer activated blue lights and the
OL,17,Fsiren of their patrol vehicle, which
OL,18,Frecorded Lowrey travelling at only
OL,19,F10mph in darkness at one stage during
OL,20,Fa 16-minute incident.
