OL,3,CWATCH: 10mph danger driver handed
OL,4,Cprison sentence
OL,6,FEven after the Focus clipped a kerb
OL,7,Fand had tyres punctured by a police
OL,8,Fstinging device, Lowrey drove on until
OL,9,Fhe was forced to a stop against a wall
OL,10,Fas other officers intervened. He was
OL,11,Farrested and taken to a police station
OL,12,Fwhere he refused to provided an
OL,13,Fevidential sample, and shouted abuse.
OL,15,FLowrey, previously of Distington,
OL,16,Fadmitted dangerous driving, aggravated
OL,17,Fvehicle taking, failing to provide a
OL,18,Fspecimen, no insurance and driving
OL,19,Fotherwise than in accordance with a
OL,20,Flicence.
