OL,3,CWATCH: 10mph danger driver handed
OL,4,Cprison sentence
OL,6,FPassing sentence, Judge Nicholas
OL,7,FBarker said he had "little hesitation"
OL,8,Fin finding that Lowrey was "heavily
OL,9,Fintoxicated" during the police
OL,10,Fpursuit. "This was a determined
OL,11,Fattempt, by you, to evade the police
OL,12,Fover what was in fact a lengthy
OL,13,Fpursuit," concluded the judge, who
OL,14,Fimposed an immediate prison sentence.
OL,16,FLowrey must serve a 30-month driving
OL,17,Fban when released and must pass an
OL,18,Fextended test before being able to
OL,19,Fdrive on public roads.
